              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
              <!-- Achievement 1 -->
              <div class="bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-900/80 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-purple-600 text-white text-2xl mb-6">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-accent-dark dark:text-accent-light">Enterprise Transformation</h3>
                <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Successfully led Google Workspace to Microsoft 365 migration for 180+ staff with zero downtime, integrating 5 legacy systems.</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-sm">Zero downtime during migration</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-sm">5 legacy systems consolidated</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-sm">90% reduction in data loss risk</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Achievement 2 -->
              <div class="bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-900/80 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-400 text-white text-2xl mb-6">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-accent-dark dark:text-accent-light">Financial Analytics</h3>
                <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Built sophisticated Power BI dashboards for real-time financial forecasting that revealed $1.2M in unbilled services.</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-sm">$1.2M in unbilled services identified</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-sm">Real-time forecast dashboards</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-sm">25% improved financial accuracy</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Achievement 3 -->
              <div class="bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-900/80 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-white text-2xl mb-6">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-accent-dark dark:text-accent-light">AI Implementation</h3>
                <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Launched enterprise-wide OpenAI workflows that save 20+ hours weekly and integrated AI into financial forecasting.</p>
